Body-132999733.html\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"90\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/images/90*90/voa-chinese-Lenin-Mausoleum-1nov11-230.jpg\" width=\"90\" /></a><br />\n<h3><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111101-Russian-will-Bury-Lenin-Body-132999733.html\">俄东正教会：下葬列宁仅是时间问题</a> <img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-audio.gif\" width=\"14\" /><img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-comment-gray.gif\" width=\"12\" /></h3>\n<p>俄罗斯东正教会表示，莫斯科红场的列宁尸体会很快下葬，这仅是个时间问题。社会民调显示，大多数俄国人主张下葬列宁。前苏联总统戈尔巴乔夫说，俄罗斯正在朝下葬列宁这个方向前进。</p>\n<div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111101-enbalmed-leaders-133040498.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%A3%BA%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E5%85%9A%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111101-enbalmed-leaders-133040498.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=